Displays info for a specific package

USAGE: {{#cyan}}axway pm view <package[@version]> [options] [<field[.subfield]>]{{/cyan}}

VIEW ARGUMENTS:
  {{#cyan}}package      {{/cyan}}  The package name and version to view
  {{#cyan}}filter       {{/cyan}}  Display specific package fields

VIEW OPTIONS:
  {{#cyan}}--json       {{/cyan}}  Outputs package info as JSON

GLOBAL OPTIONS:
  {{#cyan}}--no-banner  {{/cyan}}  Suppress the banner
  {{#cyan}}--no-color   {{/cyan}}  Disable colors
  {{#cyan}}-h, --help   {{/cyan}}  Displays the help screen
  {{#cyan}}-v, --version{{/cyan}}  Outputs the version
